{"tid":1725291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好感到灰心同失敗","createTime":"2019-11-15T16:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:44:48.000Z","uid":1988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8010b540d77c625f81aed024dfff66a3954f626","tid":1725291,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月嚟<br />\n我哋不停反省 思考 進化<br />\n呢個係我哋唯一可以贏到popo同共產黨嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n為咗學習企開d 唔好咁迫<br />\n為咗學習點樣起rb<br />\n為咗學習應付狗嘅攻勢<br />\n<br />\n我哋犧牲咗幾多位手足？<br />\n用咗幾多血淚，幾多條暴動罪去學習<br />\n<br />\n今次中大嘅戰鬥<br />\n我哋捍衛咗大學嘅氣節<br />\n守護咗中大嘅家園<br />\n為之後嘅罷工戰鬥開咗個咁好嘅頭<br />\n我哋根本冇輸到！<br />\n<br />\n你可以話結局唔完美<br />\n匆匆帶著遺憾咁落寞<br />\n但唔緊要<br />\n虛心反省 思考 進化<br />\nwe will come back stronger.<br />\n<br />\n最緊要大家齊上齊落<br />\n身邊手足無事 戰鬥嘅意志仍然旺盛<br />\n嚟緊仲有大把戰鬥等著我哋"},{"pid":"9dc7c61ec41a8f5c777d97a5f1c47f410c7539d5","tid":1725291,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"353541d5bd8a2442bcb3060cc66dd99b2ff6099e","tid":1725291,"uid":55005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7873e585e8e9fe89fd4a4b2e4530f6aa8653de04","tid":1725291,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:10:56.000Z","msg":"講得好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ee1042c1fccfffc7a7d406347b9756991666ef","tid":1725291,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"保持冷靜和思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919048c4b04b3a84690c76268c1eb510cd7fa53b","tid":1725291,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T17:38:4